      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTON MORIALTA (1) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten half a length (22.84) behind Suntory Lilac at Geelong. Can measure up this time. KISS FOR CASH (8) comes off an average effort last start when fifth at The Meadows over 525m behind Star Note (30.49) in a Maiden H. Was in the money the start prior. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. YALE TURN (3) has missed the frame at his last couple but wasn't beaten far three back when second (30.31) at The Meadows in a Maiden. Key player on best and worth another try. KIWI DUNKELD (2) is a newcomer from the Korie-Lee Heinrich kennel. Drawn favourably and can capitalise. Can sneak into the frame at his first appearance.",
